    "Table 4 contains extensive first-order and second-order interaction coefficients at 1873 K used for activity calculations.",
    "Table 5 lists equilibrium distribution coefficients (k) for BCC (δ) and FCC (γ) and diffusion coefficients for Al, N, Mn, S, Ti in both phases.",
